== 流行文化 ==
小意大利是在小說《[[教父_(小說)|教父]]》和改編它的[[教父_(電影)|三部電影]]中描繪的虛構[[柯里昂家族|柯里昂犯罪家族]]的地方。這裡也是由[[羅拔·迪尼路|羅拔·迪尼路]]和[[夏菲·基圖|夏菲·基圖]]主演的1973年電影《[[窮街陋巷|窮街陋巷]]》<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/2000/07/16/nyregion/little-italy-journal-reliving-mean-streets-in-open-air-screenings.html |title = Little Italy Journal; Reliving 'Mean Streets' In Open-Air Screenings |author = Edward Wong |date = 2000-07-16 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |access-date = 2018-04-25 |archive-date = 2021-03-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210310182131/https://www.nytimes.com/2000/07/16/nyregion/little-italy-journal-reliving-mean-streets-in-open-air-screenings.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>，以及由[[尚·連奴|尚·連奴]]和[[妮妲莉·寶雯|妮妲莉·寶雯]]主演的1994年電影《[[這個殺手不太冷|這個殺手不太冷]]》的故事背景<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://theconcourse.deadspin.com/the-professional-is-deeply-problematic-profoundly-cool-1702737080 |title = The Professional Is Deeply Problematic, Profoundly Cool, And Very '90s |author = Tom Breihan |date = 2015-05-15 |publisher = The Concourse |language = en |access-date = 2018-04-25 |archive-date = 2021-03-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308054812/https://theconcourse.deadspin.com/the-professional-is-deeply-problematic-profoundly-cool-1702737080 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

